# Title: Potential Product Reconnaissance Via Wmic.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali
# Date: 2023-02-14
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects the execution of WMIC in order to get a list of firewall and antivirus products
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1047
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wmic_recon_product.yml

CommandLine="*Product*" Image="*\\wmic.exe" OR OriginalFileName="wmic.exe" NOT (CommandLine IN ("* uninstall*", "* install*"))